			<div class="article-title col-sm-offset-2 col-sm-8 pv-sm">
				<h1 class="txt-f4 txt-s7 balance-text">A big leap in the credibility of India‚Äôs nuclear weapons capability</h1>
			</div>
			<div class="article-author pv-md col-sm-offset-3 col-sm-6">
															<a class="txt-dn txt-f1 txt-s3 txt-tu" href="/the-interpreter/contributors/articles/samuel-bashfield">
							Samuel Bashfield
						</a>
												</div>
							<div class="article-summary col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-10">
					<p class="txt-s5 txt-f1 balance-text txt-lmd">
						A successful test of India's ICBM with multiple warheads comes after an immense investment.
					</p>
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-main-image">
			<img class="article-main-image-img" src="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/interpreter_article_image/public/2024-03/GettyImages-1338553848.jpg?itok=T_qB_Gqe" alt="More warheads means more firepower (Getty Images Plus)">
              <div class="article-save-btn">
          
        </div>
      							<div class="article-main-image-caption">
					More warheads means more firepower (Getty Images Plus)
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="clearfix">
			<div class="txt-center pv-md">
				<span class="txt-muted">
					Published 19 Mar 2024&nbsp;
				</span>

									<ul class="article-tags d-ib list-unstyled">
													<li class="article-tag d-ib">
								<a href="/the-interpreter/archive?issue=321" class="txt-muted txt-dn">
									India
								</a>
							</li>
													<li class="article-tag d-ib">
								<a href="/the-interpreter/archive?issue=233" class="txt-muted txt-dn">
									Nuclear Weapons
								</a>
							</li>
											</ul>
				
								
				
							</div>


			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1"><hr></div>
			</div>

			<div class="row article-body">
				<div class="col-md-offset-1 col-md-1">
					<div class="pv-md article-share pin" data-pin data-bounds=".article-body">
            <ul class="list-unstyled clearfix">
    <li>
      <a class="txt-dn" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.lowyinstitute.org/the-interpreter/big-leap-credibility-india-s-nuclear-weapons-capability" onclick="window.open(this.href, '', 'width=600, height=300');return false;" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <i class="icon icon-social-facebook"></i>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a class="txt-dn" href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="window.open('http://www.twitter.com/share?text=‚ÄúA+big+leap+in+the+credibility+of+India%E2%80%99s+nuclear+weapons+capability‚Äù&amp;url=https://www.lowyinstitute.org/the-interpreter/big-leap-credibility-india-s-nuclear-weapons-capability','','width=600, height=400')">
        <i class="icon icon-social-twitter"></i>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a class="txt-dn" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https://www.lowyinstitute.org/the-interpreter/big-leap-credibility-india-s-nuclear-weapons-capability&amp;title=A+big+leap+in+the+credibility+of+India%E2%80%99s+nuclear+weapons+capability&amp;summary=A+big+leap+in+the+credibility+of+India%E2%80%99s+nuclear+weapons+capability&amp;source=" onclick="javascript:window.open(this.href,
    '', 'menubar=no,toolbar=no,resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,height=600,width=600');return false;" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <i class="icon icon-social-linkedin"></i>
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a class="txt-dn" href="mailto:?subject=A+big+leap+in+the+credibility+of+India%E2%80%99s+nuclear+weapons+capability&amp;body=https://www.lowyinstitute.org/the-interpreter/big-leap-credibility-india-s-nuclear-weapons-capability">
        <i class="icon icon-mail"></i>
